# Input

```md
[foo]: /url\bar\*baz "foo\"bar\baz"

[foo]

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,3 +1,3 @@
-[foo]: /url\bar*baz 'foo"bar\\baz'
+[foo]: /url\bar\*baz "foo\"bar\baz"
 
 [foo]
```

# Output

```md
[foo]: /url\bar\*baz "foo\"bar\baz"

[foo]
```
